* {{cog|bo|གྲུ||boat (of inflated hides)}} ({{zh-ref|Bodman, 1980}});
* {{w|Tamang language|Tamang}} {{m|und|tr=¹kuri|t=skin}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}});
* {{cog|bo|གོས||clothes}}, {{cog|sit-jap|ŋga||to wear}}, {{cog|txg|𗔛||to wear}} ({{zh-ref|Zhang, Jacques and Lai, 2019}}; {{zh-ref|Sims, 2025}}), all from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*gwə|t=to wear}}.

